Add supertest integration tests for AI API routes

- Extract Express app into server/app.ts for testable imports
- Add shared test helpers and fixtures (tests/api/helpers.ts)
- Add integration tests for all 6 AI routes:
  editNodes, answerAboutNodes, cleanData, summarizeData,
  diagnoseNodes, explainNode
- Install supertest and @types/supertest as dev dependencies
- 35 new tests covering validation, mock AI responses, no-key
  fallbacks, and error handling
